categories: Category:Unidentified Jedi of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: A Cathar served as a Jedi during the Great Hunt. He accompanied Shaela Nuur, Duron Qel-Droma, and Guun Han Saresh during the Cleansing of Tatooine. During the cleansing, he was killed by a Terentatek. His body was then taken back to Dantooine.
